# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is inspired by **Keep a Changelog** and this project follows semantic versioning during development.

---

## [0.0.2-alpha] - 2026-03-18

### Added
- Added initial batch localization support for dashboard-related launchers
- Added new UI namespaces for localized batch menus
- Added multilingual coverage for all supported application languages

### Changed
- Standardized project file headers and internal comments
- Consolidated project architecture and runtime folder conventions
- Refactored core Python scripts related to database setup, synchronization, status, and i18n checks
- Improved dashboard localization flow with centralized language loading
- Updated batch launchers to align with project structure and i18n rules
- Expanded and synchronized application language files across all supported locales

### Notes
- The project remains in early alpha
- English remains the source of truth for i18n
- Fallback to English is preserved for incomplete or technical cases

---

## [0.0.1-alpha] - 2026-03-15

Initial public foundation of the project.

### Added

- Added initial repository structure
- project documentation files (`README.md`, `LICENSE`, `CHANGELOG`, `VERSION`)
- Git and local environment protection files (`.gitignore`, `.env.example`)
- base folders for configuration, dashboard, modules, scripts, SQL, databases and logs
- initial development tooling configuration (`.editorconfig`, `pyproject.toml`)

### Notes

- this version represents the first public alpha state of the project
- the architecture is still under active restructuring
